 * @file
 * Custom footer template for SACDA theme.
 *
 * Available variables:
 * - page: The page render array containing footer regions.
 * - footer_logo: Logo URL for the footer (if provided).
 * - site_name: The site name.
 * - current_year: The current year for copyright.
 * - footer_partners: Array of partner items with name, image, link, weight.
 * - footer_social_links: Array of social link items with title, icon, link, weight.
 */
#}

